{"tid":984946,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【蝗語學生】逾10學生霸枱打機　興奮狂爆粗　食客斥煩擾","createTime":"2019-01-17T08:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T08:34:31.000Z","uid":225464,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"781680cdf35535d54c0fae280087e9c44bda925b","tid":984946,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T08:12:07.000Z","msg":"<strong>逾10學生霸枱打機　興奮狂爆粗　食客斥煩擾</strong><br />\n<br />\nLINK有片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仆你個街　係咁請操你媽<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190117/bkn-20190117154736552-0117_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190117%2Fbkn-20190117154736552-0117_00822_001.html&d=b1OF%2B0C98ImIiU9%2BlqVqRk4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=9c83d06f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190117/bkn-20190117154736552-0117_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190117/photo/bkn-20190117154736552-0117_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190117160320\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190117%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190117154736552-0117_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190117160320&h=1c6ad752&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔通個個都係電競選手？"},{"pid":"abe5c0edfe4f44cb9bea41239b4adfab30e85eb1","tid":984946,"uid":225464,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T08:12:21.000Z","msg":"電競風氣盛行，不少學生哥都會打機放鬆一下。惟近日大埔有約10名中學生聚集在快餐店打機，期間更不斷以普通話大聲喧嘩︰「我X你媽的」，惹起其他食客不滿。<br />\n<br />\n據Facebook群組「Tai Po 大埔」的貼文表示，周三（16日）約中午時分，有約10名身穿中學校服的男學生分佔2枱，手持電話正在打機。發貼者指他們枱上還放着早餐，「即係佢哋至少霸咗喺度2個鐘」。<br />\n<br />\n「食完嘢坐陣玩一陣傾吓偈唔係問題&hellip;佢哋仲要喺度大聲叫囂，粗口橫飛，咩人都唔肯讓，你有你等佢有佢打，成間網吧咁」。從其影片可見，學生哥玩得正緊張之時，不時以普通話驚呼︰「我X你媽的」、「我X」。<br />\n<br />\n有在場食客大感不滿，直認「睇唔過眼」，希望「佢哋學校好好管教吓學生」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民推斷︰「考試放早，咪約埋一齊打機囉」、「唔溫書，去打機」、「聽日肯定會有人反映，有好戲睇」。有人亦慨嘆：「我到底係咪自己過咗關唔知」、「仲有補習阿sir霸兩三張枱同學生補習」。"},{"pid":"e406a536a225cc32c7ba36eb3f2155b255dafa27","tid":984946,"uid":99700,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T08:20:30.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94be55ee1e0ae87f453a9ca8f0f536a8c506d6bb","tid":984946,"uid":92983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T08:33:10.000Z","msg":"焦土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c0885662fbd5383f76aedf619a95f953272b92","tid":984946,"uid":179467,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T08:34:31.000Z","msg":"中學雞個個都係度裝逼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}